snippet.title: Orbitron: Revolution Trailer
snippet.description:
http://marketplace.xbox.com/Product/Orbitron-Revolution/66acd000-77fe-1000-9115-d802585509f9

Orbitron: Revolution is an Xbox Live Indie Game being submitted into Dream Build Play 2011. Developed by Firebase Industries in Vancouver, the project uses the Sunburn Engine from Synapse Gaming and features music by Audio Antics (Geometry Wars, Project Gotham Racing)
